{"tid":904609,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 推 Pixel 專用夜視模式　提供最強夜拍體驗","createTime":"2018-11-16T13:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T06:16:54.000Z","uid":97606,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0f75d83a02c63ba4955a1ede8185f0ea4a8561f6","tid":904609,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:09:50.000Z","msg":"早於今年 10 月的 Google 發布會上， Pixel 3 以機械學習及計算攝影等技術，為用家提供多種不同的梵機功能，更有不少用家表示它是最強的電話相機。如今， Google 更正式宣布，於所有 Pixel 機種的相機 App 上，推出 Night Sight 夜拍功能，為用家帶來更強的夜間攝影體驗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pixel-3-night-sight-768x432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fpixel-3-night-sight-768x432.jpg&h=094fa7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了在昏暗環境下拍攝，相機往往需要延長曝光時間及提高 ISO 進行拍攝。而 Night Sight 夜拍功能則借助演算法，並於拍照前測量用家的手震幅度及畫面中的動態元素，從而決定曝光時間。此外，手機更會同時拍攝多張照片，並將多張相片合併成一張明亮的成品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099006/org/8a6aa6d070931b7d33214aaa55e69a5a.jpg/QyobOMHulrKKtZclZop9x_hxdkQBSIjZvZjzkb2Y85E?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099006%2Forg%2F8a6aa6d070931b7d33214aaa55e69a5a.jpg%2FQyobOMHulrKKtZclZop9x_hxdkQBSIjZvZjzkb2Y85E%3Fv%3Dw800&h=3efa241b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099007/org/c5c0ec97c02231ce08019ef3ce339ced.jpg/tBMasK5ccnnCmUgvUNuJk34DoQ_goPhEHQhbjB0IW4w?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099007%2Forg%2Fc5c0ec97c02231ce08019ef3ce339ced.jpg%2FtBMasK5ccnnCmUgvUNuJk34DoQ_goPhEHQhbjB0IW4w%3Fv%3Dw800&h=9f3a175b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外， Night Sight 更可透過機械學習及類神經網路技術，自行調整相片的白平衡，為用家重現原有色彩。當用家使用 Pixel 拍照時，只需要選用有關模式，在按動快門後盡量保持靜止，即可完成拍攝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/MVIMG_20181112_193652zzzz-768x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FMVIMG_20181112_193652zzzz-768x576.jpg&h=9546ec44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_20181112_193657zzzz-768x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FIMG_20181112_193657zzzz-768x576.jpg&h=ae2c5e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據外國科技網站 The Verge 實試，可見啟動 Night Sight 後，成品照片的亮度明顯較高，更可去除黑暗環境常見的雜訊，相片品質亦十分可觀。但該網站的測試員表示， Night Sight 會讓相片看起來不再像在夜間拍攝，因此在真正的微光環境中才能完全發揮這個功能的用途。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/MVIMG_20181112_120310a-768x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FMVIMG_20181112_120310a-768x576.jpg&h=0506e266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_20181112_120316a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FIMG_20181112_120316a.jpg&h=289b6263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/MVIMG_20181112_183752ggg-768x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FMVIMG_20181112_183752ggg-768x576.jpg&h=1bf50c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_20181112_183743ggg-768x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FIMG_20181112_183743ggg-768x576.jpg&h=9368e2fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2096a8f3cc18fcfbf2aedcbed5909ee6ae88a2dd","tid":904609,"uid":161063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:21:55.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32851df749b70a98170d0aa41a12f1cbd6e3