ploads%2F2018%2F11%2FMVIMG_20181112_193652zzzz-768x576.jpg&h=9546ec44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_20181112_193657zzzz-768x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FIMG_20181112_193657zzzz-768x576.jpg&h=ae2c5e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據外國科技網站 The Verge 實試，可見啟動 Night Sight 後，成品照片的亮度明顯較高，更可去除黑暗環境常見的雜訊，相片品質亦十分可觀。但該網站的測試員表示， Night Sight 會讓相片看起來不再像在夜間拍攝，因此在真正的微光環境中才能完全發揮這個功能的用途。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/MVIMG_20181112_120310a-768x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FMVIMG_20181112_120310a-768x576.jpg&h=0506e266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_20181112_120316a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FIMG_20181112_120316a.jpg&h=289b6263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/MVIMG_20181112_183752ggg-768x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FMVIMG_20181112_183752ggg-768x576.jpg&h=1bf50c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_20181112_183743ggg-768x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FIMG_20181112_183743ggg-768x576.jpg&h=9368e2fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T14:37:35.000Z","msg":"呢個技術 印象中 sony 相機都有個類似既 6合1 相"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T23:21:12.000Z","msg":"二手科技嚟<br />\n十年前DC都有依個功能<br />\n係智能電話興咗之後<br />\n啲廠冇相機廠啲專利同技術放唔到落software先冇依個功能<br />\n其實一早已經有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:55:11.000Z","msg":"Night Sight uses a similar principle, although at full sensor resolution and not i